{"name":"Android","postlist":[{"title":"Android 四大组件","slug":"Android 四大组件","date":"2017-10-12T07:40:38.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:44:49.224Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android 四大组件.json","excerpt":"Android 系统对四大组件的过程进行了很大程度的封装，本文侧重于对四大组件工作过程的分析，通过分析他们的工作过程理解系统内部运行机制，加深我们对 Android 整体系统结构的认识。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"源码分析","path":"api/categories/源码分析.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"source code","path":"api/tags/source code.json"}]},{"title":"Android 应用架构","slug":"Android 应用架构","date":"2018-04-08T02:41:33.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:52:01.699Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android 应用架构.json","excerpt":"关于 Android 架构的讨论，MVC、MVP 和 MVVM 不绝于耳，后面又有模块化和插件化。下面主要对比前三者的异同，以及具体介绍 Google 推出的 Architecture Components 开源库。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"程序设计","path":"api/categories/程序设计.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"MVVM","path":"api/tags/MVVM.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Android 性能优化","slug":"Android 性能优化","date":"2017-11-15T05:12:21.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:47:00.422Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android 性能优化.json","excerpt":"本文主要介绍了一些 Android 的性能优化方法和程序设计的思想，在日常开发中经常使用，将有助于提高 Android 程序的性能，提升用户体验。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"性能优化","path":"api/categories/性能优化.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"optimization","path":"api/tags/optimization.json"}]},{"title":"AspectJ","slug":"AspectJ","date":"2018-03-27T06:33:19.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:51:36.017Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/AspectJ.json","excerpt":"如果说，OOP 如果是把问题划分到单个模块的话，那么 AOP 就是把涉及到众多模块的某一类问题进行统一管理。这里通过几个小例子，讲解在 Android 开发中，如何运用 AOP 的方式，进行全局切片管理，达到简洁优雅，一劳永逸的效果。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"程序设计","path":"api/categories/程序设计.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"AOP","path":"api/tags/AOP.json"},{"name":"AspectJ","path":"api/tags/AspectJ.json"}]},{"title":"Dagger2","slug":"Dagger2","date":"2018-03-06T06:00:43.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:51:09.975Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Dagger2.json","excerpt":"Dagger2 是 Dagger 的升级版，是一个依赖注入框架。Dagger2 与其他依赖注入框架不同，它是通过 apt 插件在编译阶段生成相应的注入代码。依赖注入是面向对象编程的一种设计模式，其目的是为了降低程序耦合，这个耦合就是类之间的依赖引起的。","keywords":null,"cover":"/2018/03/06/Dagger2/Dagger2/image-201804031417535.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Data Binding 的双向绑定","slug":"Data Binding 的双向绑定","date":"2018-01-05T02:15:58.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:51:36.614Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Data Binding 的双向绑定.json","excerpt":" DataBinding 支持双向绑定，能大大减少绑定 app 逻辑与 layout 文件的“胶水代码”。双向绑定，指的是将数据与界面绑定起来，当数据发生变化时会体现在界面上，反过来界面内容变化也会同步更新到数据上，使用 DataBinding 能轻松实现 MVVM 模式。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"EventBus","slug":"EventBus","date":"2017-12-27T05:52:33.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:49:13.266Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/EventBus.json","excerpt":"EventBus 基于观察者模式的 Android 事件分发总线。它使得 事件发送 和 事件接收 很好地解耦。另外使得 Android 组件之间的通信变得简单，代码变得整洁。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"OkHttp","slug":"OkHttp","date":"2017-12-08T05:34:07.000Z","updated":"2018-04-07T09:39:16.666Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/OkHttp.json","excerpt":"OkHttp 是一个高效的 HTTP 库:支持 SPDY ，共享同一个 Socke t来处理同一个服务器的所有请求如果 SPDY 不可用，则通过连接池来减少请求延时无缝的支持 GZIP 来减少数据流量缓存响应数据来减少重复的网络请求","keywords":null,"cover":"/2017/12/08/OkHttp/OkHttp/image-201804020012074.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Handler","slug":"Handler","date":"2017-11-06T05:20:17.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:46:40.397Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Handler.json","excerpt":"Handler 是 Android 消息机制的上层接口，用来解决线程之间的通信。接下来将介绍一下 Handler 的运行机制、Handler 所附带的 MessageQueue 和 Looper 的工作过程。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"源码分析","path":"api/categories/源码分析.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"source code","path":"api/tags/source code.json"}]},{"title":"Glide","slug":"Glide","date":"2017-11-30T05:24:21.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:47:40.800Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Glide.json","excerpt":"Glide 是 Google 推荐的一套快速高效的图片加载框架，功能强大且使用方便。它在使用上大致分为 with、load、into 三个步骤，接下来将分别围绕这三个方法来解析。","keywords":null,"cover":"/2017/11/30/Glide/Glide/image-201804020004200.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Retrofit","slug":"Retrofit","date":"2018-01-16T05:45:52.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:50:44.887Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Retrofit.json","excerpt":"Retrofit 是一个 RESTful 的 HTTP 网络请求框架的封装。网络请求的工作本质上是 OkHttp 完成，而 Retrofit 仅负责网络请求接口的封装。","keywords":null,"cover":"/2018/01/16/Retrofit/Retrofit/944365-72f373fbbb960b69.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"View 的事件分发机制","slug":"View 的事件分发机制","date":"2017-10-20T04:43:35.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:45:42.364Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/View 的事件分发机制.json","excerpt":"在 Android 开发中，事件分发机制是一块 Android 比较重要的知识体系，了解并熟悉整套的分发机制有助于更好的分析各种点击滑动失效问题，更好去扩展控件的事件功能和开发自定义控件。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"源码分析","path":"api/categories/源码分析.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"source code","path":"api/tags/source code.json"}]},{"title":"单例模式","slug":"单例模式","date":"2017-10-28T05:06:24.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:46:00.164Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/单例模式.json","excerpt":"单例模式算是设计模式中最容易理解，也是最容易手写代码的模式了吧。但是其中的坑却不少，所以也常作为面试题来考。本文主要对几种单例写法进行了整理。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"程序设计","path":"api/categories/程序设计.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"Design pattern","path":"api/tags/Design pattern.json"}]},{"title":"嵌套滑动机制","slug":"嵌套滑动机制","date":"2018-01-25T02:13:34.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:50:43.288Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/嵌套滑动机制.json","excerpt":"嵌套滑动一直是 Android 中比较棘手的问题，根本原因是 Android 的事件分发机制导致的。不过这个问题终于在 API 21之后有了官方的解决方法，就是嵌套滑动机制。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"源码分析","path":"api/categories/源码分析.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"source code","path":"api/tags/source code.json"}]},{"title":"Android ListView 与 RecyclerView 缓存机制","slug":"Android ListView 与 RecyclerView 缓存机制","date":"2017-12-18T06:42:33.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:46:37.500Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android ListView 与 RecyclerView 缓存机制.json","excerpt":"通过研究 RecyclerView 和 ListView 二者的缓存机制，并得到了一些较有益的“结论”。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"源码分析","path":"api/categories/源码分析.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"source code","path":"api/tags/source code.json"}]},{"title":"Android AOP","slug":"Android AOP","date":"2018-03-16T06:28:19.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:51:21.151Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android AOP.json","excerpt":"Android AOP 就是通过预编译方式和运行期动态代理实现程序功能的统一维护的一种技术。利用 AOP 可以对业务逻辑的各个部分进行隔离，从而使得业务逻辑各部分之间的耦合度降低，提高程序的可重用性，提高开发效率。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"程序设计","path":"api/categories/程序设计.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"AOP","path":"api/tags/AOP.json"}]}]}